{"article_id":"Cj5RnSZ0mCYiKuYR","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Attorney General Jeff Sessions","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Jefferson","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"( Jeff ) Beauregard SessionsSanford :","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"'It carries real weight '","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"to speak against Trump 'while in office '","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Medill dean 'deeply troubled by the vicious bullying and badgering ' of student journalists","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"Trump has considered firing official","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"who reported whistleblower complaint to Congress : report","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"MORE is in a bind","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"following public criticism from President Trump of his decision","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"to recuse himself from the Russia investigation .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"Trump ' s scathing criticism in an interview with The New York Times immediately sparked new questions","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"about whether the nation ' s top cop , one of the president ' s earliest supporters , enjoys his confidence and support .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"Sessions on Thursday made it clear","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"he has no plans","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"to leave his post ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"and several Republican lawmakers rushed to his defense .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"\" I think","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"Jeff Sessions has been and will continue to be an excellent attorney general , \"","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"said Rep. Chris Collins","depth":13},{"id":20,"text":"( R-N.Y. ) ,","depth":13},{"id":21,"text":"an early Trump supporter","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"who says","depth":14},{"id":23,"text":"he backed Sessions 's decision","depth":15},{"id":24,"text":"to recuse himself .","depth":15},{"id":25,"text":"\" I don ' t expect Jeff Sessions to resign ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"I would not want him to resign . \"","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Republicans on and off Capitol Hill marveled at the spectacle","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"of Trump","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"criticizing his own attorney general","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"- and a politician","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"seen as one of his closest allies .","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"\" They need to put this behind them , \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"said GOP strategist Matt Mackowiak , a contributor to ,","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"who added","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"that there is no benefit to Trump ' s criticism of Sessions .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"John Wood , a former U.S. attorney and chief of staff for the Department of Homeland Security in the George W. Bush administration , said","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Sessions could continue to serve","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"despite the criticism .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"But he said","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Trump ' s comments likely hurt Sessions ' s standing","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"and could make it harder for him to lead the department .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"it is to the point","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"where Sessions has lost the ability","depth":14},{"id":45,"text":"to run the department , \"","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"Trump told The New York Times in a Wednesday interview","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"that he would not have chosen Sessions","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"to serve as attorney general","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"had he known","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"he would recuse himself .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"\" How do you take a job","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"and then recuse yourself ?","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"If he would have recused himself before the job ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"I would have said ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"' Thanks , Jeff ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"but I ' m not going to take you , ' ''","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Trump told the Times .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Trump ' s comments also provided ammunition for critics","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"who say","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"he wants to squash the work of special counsel Robert Mueller","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"- the man","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"now leading the investigation into Russia 's meddling in the 2016 presidential election ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"including any possible ties between Trump campaign associates and Moscow .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Trump warned Mueller against investigating the Trump family ' s finances beyond the scope of the probe into ties between his administration and Russia .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"that ' s a violation .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"Look , this is about Russia , \"","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"Trump told the Times .","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Mueller was appointed to his position by Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"after Trump fired former FBI Director James Comey .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Rosenstein is now the top Justice official","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"overseeing Mueller ' s work .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"If Trump had a different attorney general ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"it would be easier to remove Mueller ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"since a Sessions successor would take over from Rosenstein .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Members of Congress might then appoint their own counsel","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"to lead an outside investigation , however .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"Sessions expressed confidence","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"he could carry out the mission of the Justice Department during remarks at a Thursday press conference .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"\" I have the honor","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"of serving as attorney general .","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"It 's something","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"that goes beyond any thought","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"I would have ever had for myself , \"","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Sessions said .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"\" We love this job ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"we love this department ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"and I plan to continue to do so","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"as long as that is appropriate . \"","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Sessions ducked question","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"about how he could continue in his role","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"without the confidence of the president .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"\" We ' re serving right now .","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"The work","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"we ' re doing today","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"is the kind of work","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"that we intend to continue , \"","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"the attorney general said .","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"\" I 'm totally confident","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"that we can continue to run this office in an effective way . \"","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"The White House on Thursday said","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"Trump has confidence in Sessions ,","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"but spokeswoman Sarah Huckabee Sanders added","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"that he is \" disappointed \" with Sessions ' s decision","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"to recuse himself .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"If Sessions did step down ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Rosenstein would become attorney general","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"until the Senate confirmed a new replacement .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Trump also criticized Rosenstein in the interview with The Times , suggestion","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"he was probably a Democrat","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"because he was from Baltimore .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"Rosenstein is from Philadelphia","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"but was previously the U.S. attorney for the District of Maryland .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Mackowiak said","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"if Sessions was pushed out ,","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"it would likely be a \" difficult situation. \"","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"Trump would need to find and vet a new attorney general ,","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"and the confirmation process would eat up precious time for an administration","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"that ' s without a signature legislative achievement .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"Wood said","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"he doesn ' t think","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"it will be difficult to find a new person for the position","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"because it ' s a hard job for anybody to pass up .","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"But to make a quick change would be \" disruptive \" to the Justice Department ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"If Trump decided to make a change","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"simply because he disagrees with Sessions ' s recusal decision ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"Wood said ,","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"that \" could undermine the professionalism \" of the department .","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"Sen. Richard Blumenthal","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"( D-Conn. ) ,","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"a member of the Judiciary Committee , opposed Sessions ' s nomination","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"but said","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"he \" shouldn ' t be forced to resign","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"for following ethical rules","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"- especially if he ' ll be replaced by a Trump lackey . \"","depth":9},{"id":138,"text":"\" Ultimately , this is about the rule of law , not Sessions .","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"Protecting Mueller probe 's independence & integrity is the top priority , \"","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"Blumenthal tweeted .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":281,"left":0,"right":280,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":280,"left":147,"right":279,"relat